import React from 'react'
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'

const Header = () => {
  return (
  <>
  <Navbar bg="primary" data-bs-theme="dark">
    <Container>
      <Navbar.Brand href="/">Who am I</Navbar.Brand>
      <Nav className="me-auto">
        <NavLink href="/">Favorite Hobbiess</NavLink>
        <NavLink href="/favper">Favorite Personality</NavLink>
        <NavLink href="/favcit">Favorite Cities</NavLink>
        <NavLink href="/favtour">Favorite Tourist Spots</NavLink>
        <NavLink href="/contact">Contact Info</NavLink>
        </Nav>
    </Container>
  </Navbar>
  </>
  )
}

export default Header
